name: PRADA/FW22
description: an homage to the genius of Miuccia Prada and Raf Simons, a 3d rendering fully textured, modelled and composed by the artist, I recreated a small scene from the sci-fi runway with a model wearing custom MetaScorpius x Prada garments, including the iconic white vest that is soon to be a viral fashion garment. made using Blender, Photoshop and DazStudio. Credits to artists who allowed free use of their base models for interpretation.
